    <briefdescription>
<para>RTOS wrapper for software timer support. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The timer class implements a C++ wrapper of the timer API provided by the Zephyr operating system. See details in Zephyr <linebreak/>
 <ulink url="https://docs.zephyrproject.org/latest/kernel/services/timing/timers.html">timer documentation</ulink> or in <ulink url="https://docs.zephyrproject.org/apidoc/latest/group__timer__apis.html">API documentation</ulink>. The timer class provides methods to start and stop timers. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
